[Episode 27]

4
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:11,100
Is Yuwei asleep?

5
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:23,400
I still can't believe

6
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:26,000
that you really broke up with Brother Yiming.

7
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:30,800
Yeah. How did you suddenly get this point?

8
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,500
Sister Siyu,

9
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:47,600
could it be that you are being too eager to excel?

10
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:51,600
Yeah. Can't you just take a step back?

11
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:55,200
First get married, then start a business. The order is not a big deal.

12
00:02:58,300 --> 00:03:01,100
It's not about what comes first and what comes last.

13
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:06,400
It's what he wants and what I want most

14
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,200
are different.

15
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:10,600
Can you not compromise?

16
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:17,300
I've been compromising up until today. I'm tired.

17
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,800
Is there still a possibility that you'll get back together?

18
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,600
No.

19
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:36,800
If you want to cry, just cry.

20
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,600
I don't have time to cry.

21
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:54,410
There's still so much work waiting for me to do.

22
00:03:56,200 --> 00:04:00,200
Fortunately, I still have work.

23
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:04,540
If you guys are really breaking up,

24
00:04:04,540 --> 00:04:06,970
then you need to figure out the debts between you two.

25
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:10,400
What debt?

26
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:14,200
What's going to happen to the house they bought together? How about the mortgage?

27
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,830
You go talk to him.

28
00:04:17,830 --> 00:04:20,000
I don't have time.

29
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:53,910
This idea is quite good.

30
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:58,200
You can take care of each other.

31
00:04:58,200 --> 00:05:01,100
You can live at my house to save money.

32
00:05:01,730 --> 00:05:04,110
But let me tell you clearly.

33
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:08,600
If I have an important date, then you have to go stay at a hotel.

34
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:12,900
Also, you can't force me to

35
00:05:12,900 --> 00:05:16,000
memorize words, write essays, and do my homework every day like when we were younger.

36
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:20,000
Also, you can't call me a coquettish girl every time I dress up.

37
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,200
More importantly, you can't report everything I do to my mom.

38
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:24,400
I won't.

39
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:33,900
Zhizhi, what do you plan to do?

40
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,630
Divorce.

41
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:51,700
I heard something happened to Liu Yang.

42
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:53,800
That girl betrayed Liu Yang.

43
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:56,900
Liu Yang really ended things with her this time.

44
00:06:02,130 --> 00:06:04,810
So what?

45
00:06:04,810 --> 00:06:07,000
Once you find out

46
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,800
about some things

47
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:13,100
you can't pretend to be oblivious.

48
00:06:13,900 --> 00:06:15,600
What things?

49
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:18,040
Liu Yang is very stiff, awkward,

50
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:20,200
and a dumb man.

51
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,100
He doesn't know how to be romantic

52
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,800
and doesn't know how to take care of people.

53
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:32,800
But when I saw him together with Wei Yayun, I realized

54
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:40,100
that he does know how to be romantic

55
00:06:41,300 --> 00:06:43,900
and does know how to take care of people.

56
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:48,700
It just depends on who he's with.

57
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:58,690
During these five years of marriage,

58
00:07:01,180 --> 00:07:03,820
our lives have been quite hard;

59
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:07,300
however, I was willing to go through the hardships

60
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,200
because he loved me

61
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:13,600
and I loved him.

62
00:07:15,580 --> 00:07:18,420
I was willing to giving everything up for him.

63
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,600
But in reality,

64
00:07:23,770 --> 00:07:26,220
I was just lying to myself.

65
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:29,600
He didn't love me.

66
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:35,200
He didn't see me as a lover or a wife.

67
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:37,200
During this whole time,

68
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:42,700
he just saw me as a nanny.

69
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:47,000
But even now,

70
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:50,000
you still go to the hospital to take care of him every day.

71
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:59,300
Even though I am completely disappointed in him,

72
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:06,600
he's still Yuwei's dad.

73
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:11,700
Zhizhi, you're too kind.

74
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,600
In a marriage,

75
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:19,600
kindness can't be exchanged for sincerity.

76
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:23,600
Even if you do get sincerity,

77
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:28,200
it will be destroyed by the pressures of life.

78
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:35,200
Enough. You two stop talking.

79
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:37,800
If you keep saying things like this,

80
00:08:37,800 --> 00:08:40,400
all of us will become dissatisfied housewives.

81
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:44,500
Isn't it merely five years of your youth wasted for a bastard?

82
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:46,400
It's fine.

83
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:51,000
In the next five years, we can live happily to make up for the past five years.

84
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:54,000
And you! Isn't it just a mere break up?

85
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:56,900
It hasn't even been half a year and I've already broken up twice!

86
00:08:56,900 --> 00:09:00,200
Look!  Have I been depressed or sad?

87
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:03,500
You win in the end only if you fight on despite repeated setbacks.

88
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:05,800
Let's empty this bottle of wine.

89
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,500
Pour it.

90
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:18,100
Okay. Mine.

91
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:24,400
I'm announcing that we are going to

92
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:27,600
leave all of our sorrows, problems, and anger

93
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:30,000
in the present.

94
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:32,400
Tomorrow is a new day!

95
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:35,200
- Cheers! 
 - Cheers.

96
00:10:38,790 --> 00:10:40,390
Is she okay?

97
00:10:41,020 --> 00:10:42,790
She's really well.

98
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,500
How is her business venture going?

99
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:50,600
You're not even supporting her, so just don't ask.

100
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:58,900
She hopes... that you will sell the house

101
00:10:58,900 --> 00:11:01,300
and return her the down payment she payed.

102
00:11:03,300 --> 00:11:06,710
If we sell the house then we can't buy it back.

103
00:11:06,710 --> 00:11:08,800
So how about we don't sell it?

104
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:11,400
She really needs money right now though.

105
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:15,460
I'll figure something out.

106
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:20,800
I asked the agent and he said that that house has appreciated in value.

107
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:23,700
If you sell it, you have to return at least ¥800,000 to her.

108
00:11:28,100 --> 00:11:29,800
Xiaoling,

109
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:33,200
that house has only appreciated ¥300,000 in total.

110
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,600
I know.

111
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:39,200
Also, Siyu paid ¥500,000 in total at that time.

112
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:41,600
She's been with you for 5 years.

113
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:44,400
Shouldn't you compensate her?

114
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:51,900
But I don't have that much money to give her right now.

115
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:55,170
Then write an IOU.

116
00:11:56,390 --> 00:11:59,930
I... asked for an additional ¥300,000 for you.

117
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:03,200
Who told you to do that?

118
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:06,000
I was helping you to fight for your rights and interests.

119
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:08,200
How is that fighting for my rights and interests?

120
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:10,200
This is blackmailing.

121
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:12,800
How is that blackmailing?

122
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:15,000
It's very clearly written on the house deed

123
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,800
that each of you owns half of the house.

124
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:19,000
Asking for ¥800,000 is not too much at all.

125
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:22,900
Besides, we need to get some kind of compensation for your youth!

126
00:12:22,900 --> 00:12:25,010
If I knew you had those thoughts,

127
00:12:25,010 --> 00:12:28,000
then I wouldn't have let you go!

128
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:31,000
From now on, I won't meddle into your business.

129
00:13:19,140 --> 00:13:22,660
Let's change the house deed tomorrow.

130
00:14:02,980 --> 00:14:05,630
I don't have ¥800,000 to give you right now.

131
00:14:10,770 --> 00:14:13,110
We can talk about it after we do the paperwork.

132
00:14:22,270 --> 00:14:23,850
Okay.

133
00:14:30,820 --> 00:14:32,540
I was clearly helping her,

134
00:14:32,540 --> 00:14:34,320
yet she lectured me.

135
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:37,110
Have you ever met such an ungrateful person before?

136
00:14:37,110 --> 00:14:39,180
Of course, I have.

137
00:14:40,470 --> 00:14:42,290
Last time, in front of the art museum,

138
00:14:42,290 --> 00:14:45,220
I helped a woman get out of the grasp of an asshole,

139
00:14:45,220 --> 00:14:47,210
but she also scolded me.

140
00:14:47,210 --> 00:14:49,200
Who are you talking about?

141
00:14:49,790 --> 00:14:53,420
I'm saying that the two of you are pretty much the same, you can't really judge each other.

142
00:14:57,530 --> 00:14:59,500
Then again,

143
00:14:59,500 --> 00:15:02,180
Chen Yiming is my bro.

144
00:15:02,180 --> 00:15:04,850
You asked for ¥300,000 for no reason. That's a bit harsh.

145
00:15:04,850 --> 00:15:07,530
How is it for no reason?

146
00:15:07,530 --> 00:15:11,170
He hurt Siyu and I helped her get compensation. What's wrong with that?

147
00:15:11,170 --> 00:15:13,490
Wasn't Chen Yiming also hurt?

148
00:15:13,490 --> 00:15:15,920
I saw him yesterday.

149
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:18,950
He lost a ton of weight.

150
00:15:18,950 --> 00:15:20,780
He deserves it.

151
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:25,570
If you want my opinion, this really isn't Yiming's fault.

152
00:15:25,570 --> 00:15:28,150
Then are you blaming Li Siyu?

153
00:15:28,150 --> 00:15:31,020
- Li Siyu did act a little too crazy. 
 - Who's crazy?!

154
00:15:31,020 --> 00:15:33,350
You were just saying how she was ungrateful!

155
00:15:33,350 --> 00:15:35,320
I can insult her, but you can't!

156
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:39,060
Fine, fine, fine.

157
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:49,860
Do you think the two of them will be able to make up?

158
00:15:51,380 --> 00:15:55,090
Li Siyu is going to have to change for that to happen.

159
00:15:55,090 --> 00:15:57,640
Otherwise, it will be like last time.

160
00:15:57,640 --> 00:15:59,840
They'll get back together and split again.

161
00:16:01,470 --> 00:16:04,520
Then do you think that Chen Yiming doesn't have to change?

162
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:06,410
That's true.

163
00:16:06,410 --> 00:16:09,650
Compared to me, Chen Yiming indeed is

164
00:16:09,650 --> 00:16:12,040
not as warm, handsome, or interesting;

165
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:16,050
but overall, he's considered perfect.

166
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:21,920
Eat a kebob, eat a kebob.

167
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:23,670
I can't eat spicy things for a month.

168
00:16:23,670 --> 00:16:25,260
How come?

169
00:16:25,260 --> 00:16:28,440
I had an injection, and the doctor says I need to avoid certain foods.

170
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:31,630
No way! You look like this yet you went to get injections?

171
00:16:31,630 --> 00:16:35,710
Even though I'm beautiful,  I will eventually get old.

172
00:16:35,710 --> 00:16:38,420
Why are you afraid to be old?

173
00:16:38,420 --> 00:16:41,530
Isn't there a good song about it?

174
00:16:41,530 --> 00:16:48,150
♪ How many people can love your appearance when you were young? ♪

175
00:16:48,150 --> 00:16:53,750
♪ But who will not care about the cruel changes that come with time? ♪

176
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:59,360
♪ How many people can come and go from your life? ♪

177
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:05,260
♪ Know I'll be by your side in this lifetime ♪

178
00:17:05,260 --> 00:17:06,930
Are you touched?

179
00:17:07,950 --> 00:17:09,660
Why not?

180
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:13,490
If I got old, and you were the only one by my side,

181
00:17:13,490 --> 00:17:15,520
then I would be such a failure.

182
00:17:15,520 --> 00:17:18,230
Then having whom by your side makes you feel like you aren't a failure?

183
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:21,750
He at least has to be a silver-haired

184
00:17:21,750 --> 00:17:24,960
and charming retired billionaire.

185
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:27,220
Aren't you just describing me in fifty years?

186
00:17:27,220 --> 00:17:29,200
You?

187
00:17:29,990 --> 00:17:32,990
What are you laughing at? Are you looking down on me?

188
00:17:32,990 --> 00:17:36,740
You should do something that makes me not look down on you then!

189
00:17:37,660 --> 00:17:39,680
Deal.

190
00:17:59,940 --> 00:18:03,270
Now the house only belongs to you.

191
00:18:05,050 --> 00:18:07,150
I will transfer ¥500,000 to you first.

192
00:18:07,150 --> 00:18:09,810
