204
00:19:25,020 --> 00:19:27,670
No, you aren't wrong. The things you want aren't wrong either.

205
00:19:27,670 --> 00:19:29,640
It's just that I—

206
00:19:32,380 --> 00:19:34,050
It's just...

207
00:19:34,820 --> 00:19:37,800
