00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:27,000
I think you can try it, too.

262
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:29,200
No time, no money, no interest.

263
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:31,000
I'm serious.

264
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:33,590
Even if you can't find someone to be with for the rest of your life,

265
00:25:33,590 --> 00:25:35,400
you can find someone who will help start your business.

266
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:37,700
Right? Right?

267
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:14,600
What's wrong?

268
00:26:18,900 --> 00:26:21,100
Chen Yiming transferred ¥800,000 to you?

269
00:26:21,100 --> 00:26:23,700
I guess he does have a conscience after all.

270
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,800
Do you have liquor?

271
00:26:28,800 --> 00:26:31,400
Do you want to die? Do you not want your stomach?

272
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:36,000
I will look for it for you.

273
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:46,900
[Available Balance: ¥316.99]

274
00:26:59,600 --> 00:27:01,600
[Available Balance: ¥118.00]

275
00:27:13,700 --> 00:27:16,300
[Available Balance: RBM 0.00]

276
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:22,700
If you don't need any other service, please take out your card.

277
00:27:50,300 --> 00:27:52,190
Yuwei,

278
00:27:52,190 --> 00:27:54,800
Mom wants to talk to you about something.

279
00:27:57,400 --> 00:28:01,400
We won't buy new shoes for now. Wear the old ones for now.

280
00:28:01,400 --> 00:28:04,000
But the teacher said

281
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:06,600
that my dance shoes are already battered,

282
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:09,100
and need new ones.

283
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:12,700
I will help you patch them up.

284
00:28:12,700 --> 00:28:17,200
The other kids are all wearing new dance shoes.

285
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:22,600
If I patch up your old ones, you'll still be able to dance.

286
00:28:22,600 --> 00:28:26,100
I want new dance shoes, too.

287
00:28:33,900 --> 00:28:35,800
I don't have enough money right now.

288
00:28:35,800 --> 00:28:39,200
Didn't you just take money from the bank?

289
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:41,600
This is for your dad's hospital fee,

290
00:28:41,600 --> 00:28:44,400
and it's also for your preschool fees,

291
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:46,000
and our electricity bill,

292
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:49,600
water bill, gas bill, and phone bill.

293
00:28:49,600 --> 00:28:53,500
Doesn't Daddy get money every month?

294
00:28:54,600 --> 00:28:58,400
Daddy is in the hospital right now. He has no money.

295
00:28:58,400 --> 00:29:01,400
Then is your money enough?

296
00:29:07,570 --> 00:29:10,110
You don't have to worry about that.

297
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:13,600
Mommy, I have money.

298
00:29:13,600 --> 00:29:15,600
What money do you have?

299
00:29:17,800 --> 00:29:22,000
Today, I was the first to finish eating and doing classwork.

300
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:25,600
The teacher awarded us this to use at the fairytale hut

301
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:29,300
to buy crayons and ribbons.

302
00:29:33,600 --> 00:29:36,200
These little coupons can't buy dance shoes.

303
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:37,600
I don't want dance shoes anymore.

304
00:29:37,600 --> 00:29:41,200
Mommy, you can have this money to spend.

305
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:48,220
In the future,

306
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:51,600
Mommy will buy you lots and lots of new dance shoes.

307
00:30:07,800 --> 00:30:09,600
What do you mean?

308
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:13,400
I've really never met someone like you before.

309
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:16,300
You are basically asking me to pay for your renovations.

310
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:20,600
¥26.5.

311
00:30:20,600 --> 00:30:23,800
Ms. Li, you're a boss now.

312
00:30:23,800 --> 00:30:27,400
Negotiating the price by ¥0.5 or ¥1... is there a point?

313
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:30,200
Brother, I also know that it doesn't really make a difference.

314
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:33,200
I also want to be able to magnanimously be able to wave my hand and say "Sure, let's do that,"

315
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:35,600
but my budget doesn't allow me to do that.

316
00:30:35,600 --> 00:30:37,400
Not just ¥0.5 or ¥1.

317
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:40,400
Right now, I really want to split ¥0.01 in half to spend.

318
00:30:40,400 --> 00:30:42,600
Well, we also need to earn money and eat.

319
00:30:42,600 --> 00:30:44,600
Nowadays, a bento that looks just a little bit decent is already ¥15.

320
00:30:44,600 --> 00:30:47,100
For lunch, I had a bento that only cost ¥8 each.

321
00:30:48,100 --> 00:30:51,600
Ms. Li, how much money can you pay?

322
00:30:51,600 --> 00:30:55,000
My construction budget is only  ¥300,000.

323
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:59,000
Not a single construction company in Shanghai would accept this job for that budget.

324
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:03,000
The lowest I can go... ¥580,000.

325
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:04,900
¥302,000.

326
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:08,800
If I had known earlier, I wouldn't have even come.

327
00:31:08,800 --> 00:31:11,300
Aren't you just wasting my time?

328
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:45,100
President Wang.

329
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:56,100
How come you've been staying up late so often recently?

330
00:31:58,580 --> 00:32:00,390
No, I haven't.

331
00:32:05,400 --> 00:32:07,500
How are you and Siyu?

332
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:13,700
We broke up.

333
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:30,600
How about I invite her out, and you two can talk some more?

334
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:34,500
There's no need. It's fine the way things are right now.

335
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:38,040
We are both free now

336
00:32:38,040 --> 00:32:40,000
and relieved now.

337
00:32:42,500 --> 00:32:45,400
You don't look relieved at all.

338
00:32:49,500 --> 00:32:52,400
Perhaps, I-I-

339
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:55,800
I'm not used to- used to being relieved.

340
00:32:58,800 --> 00:33:00,800
This is my stop, President Wang.

341
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:05,200
Yiming!

342
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:11,000
If you really want to be free, then you must let it go completely.

343
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:16,900
If you want someone to talk to, I'm always here.

344
00:33:19,200 --> 00:33:21,600
Thank you, Sister Ziru.

345
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:25,300
I'm leaving now.

346
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:42,800
This here, we can finish this today.

347
00:33:43,800 --> 00:33:46,300
- How about over here? 
 - Don't worry.

348
00:33:46,300 --> 00:33:49,100
We can definitely finish by the end of this month.

349
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:55,800
Please make way.

350
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:58,400
Boss Li.

351
00:33:58,400 --> 00:34:00,000
Here!

352
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:03,100
Sister Siyu.

353
00:34:03,800 --> 00:34:05,600
Zhizhi?

354
00:34:05,600 --> 00:34:07,200
Over there.

355
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:15,980
If we talk here, it's quieter and cleaner.

356
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:19,200
How come you're dressed like a construction worker?

357
00:34:19,200 --> 00:34:21,500
I am one right now.

358
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:25,000
You're not doing this personally, are you?

359
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:27,000
Doing it personally saves money.

360
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:29,200
Then what is the construction company for?

361
00:34:29,200 --> 00:34:33,200
The construction company wouldn't make any money with my budget so they rejected it.

362
00:34:33,200 --> 00:34:36,600
I found my own workers to do it.

363
00:34:37,300 --> 00:34:39,400
Will it work out?

364
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:42,500
I don't have money so I have to make it work.

365
00:34:43,600 --> 00:34:45,400
Why were you looking for me?

366
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:49,600
Nothing, I just wanted to see if you needed any help.

367
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:55,300
I'm still short ¥1 million here.

368
00:34:55,300 --> 00:34:57,500
How about you make it up for me?

369
00:34:58,900 --> 00:35:01,300
I'm joking.

370
00:35:03,100 --> 00:35:06,500
- Miss Li, give me a hand! 
 - Coming!

371
00:35:06,500 --> 00:35:08,600
- Go work. 
 - Then I'll leave you here.

372
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:10,700
Be safe!

373
00:35:42,790 --> 00:35:46,790
GM Pan, is there something you need to discuss with me?

374
00:35:46,790 --> 00:35:51,480
Nothing. I was reorganizing my cabinet just now,

375
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:54,010
and I found something.

376
00:35:54,010 --> 00:35:56,450
It made me especially touched.

377
00:36:11,090 --> 00:36:14,560
Take a close look. This tie is yours.

378
00:36:14,560 --> 00:36:18,040
- Mine? 
 - Did you forget?

379
00:36:18,040 --> 00:36:23,570
At that time, Lubao was just founded. I was going to visit a senior.

380
00:36:23,570 --> 00:36:27,910
You took this tie off and tied it on me.

381
00:36:27,910 --> 00:36:31,460
At the time, you even said

382
00:36:31,460 --> 00:36:35,460
"GM Pan, you are Lubao's representative."

383
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:39,740
"I can be a little disheveled, but you must be glamorous."

384
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:42,750
I think I remember that.

385
00:36:43,820 --> 00:36:46,210
After we'd successfully started the business,

386
00:36:47,100 --> 00:36:49,290
I bought a lot of ties,

387
00:36:50,110 --> 00:36:54,790
but this one is the only one I kept. I didn't have the heart to exchange it.

388
00:36:54,790 --> 00:36:57,980
It reminds me of your contributions to Lubao

389
00:36:57,980 --> 00:37:02,760
and our friendship forged by working hard together.

390
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:05,410
That's something that happened over ten years ago.

391
00:37:05,410 --> 00:37:09,080
Yes. Over ten years ago.

392
00:37:09,990 --> 00:37:13,800
At that time, I worked with the technicians

393
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:17,320
staying up night after night in the lab.

394
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:21,730
You and the sales team went around all of China.

395
00:37:21,730 --> 00:37:24,570
That's how we have this business today.

396
00:37:24,570 --> 00:37:27,760
I remember I had to go on a business trip to Zhengzhou.

397
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:30,460
Before leaving, your hair was all black.

398
00:37:30,460 --> 00:37:34,820
I was gone for less than a month, but when I came back, all of your hair turned white!

399
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:39,680
I also remembered that out of the 365 days in the year,

400
00:37:39,680 --> 00:37:42,720
you were on business trips for 300 days.

401
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:45,420
The other sixty days,

402
00:37:45,420 --> 00:37:49,060
you were mostly working overtime.

403
00:37:49,060 --> 00:37:51,100
Because of this,

404
00:37:51,100 --> 00:37:54,800
your ex-wife divorced you, right?

405
00:37:56,770 --> 00:37:59,580
We gave up too much for Lubao.

406
00:37:59,580 --> 00:38:03,700
Yes. We've both gave up too much for Lubao,

407
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:05,960
but the friendship between the two of us

408
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:08,680
can never be replaced by anyone.

409
00:38:09,590 --> 00:38:11,410
You're right.

410
00:38:14,200 --> 00:38:15,930
Sit.

411
00:38:22,220 --> 00:38:24,920
We've been very busy these past two years.

412
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:27,160
We've interacted a lot less than before.

413
00:38:27,160 --> 00:38:29,250
The company is getting bigger and bigger.

414
00:38:29,250 --> 00:38:33,320
The market changed, and we started to disagree with each other.

415
00:38:34,630 --> 00:38:36,690
Fang Zhan, it's okay.

416
00:38:37,720 --> 00:38:39,930
Here,

417
00:38:39,930 --> 00:38:42,380
in my heart,

418
00:38:42,380 --> 00:38:45,720
you have always been my best brother,

419
00:38:45,720 --> 00:38:48,740
companion, and partner.

420
00:38:50,250 --> 00:38:52,320
Yes.

421
00:38:52,320 --> 00:38:56,660
It was so hard in the past, yet we got through it.

422
00:38:56,660 --> 00:38:58,980
In the future, it might be even harder,

423
00:38:58,980 --> 00:39:02,180
but let us get through it together. Okay?

424
00:39:07,520 --> 00:39:10,730
GM Pan, to tell you the truth,

425
00:39:11,620 --> 00:39:13,740
I'm a little tired.

426
00:39:13,740 --> 00:39:15,500
Why?

427
00:39:18,450 --> 00:39:21,590
Nowadays, doing business is so hard.

428
00:39:21,590 --> 00:39:24,600
We can invest hundreds of millions, but in a year,

429
00:39:24,600 --> 00:39:26,590
we can only earn a few million.

430
00:39:26,590 --> 00:39:28,470
Something that might be hard to hear,

431
00:39:28,470 --> 00:39:31,120
buying a house would appreciate faster than this.

432
00:39:40,060 --> 00:39:42,140
Fang Zhan, Fang Zhan.

433
00:39:42,140 --> 00:39:46,880
When we invested in this industry back then, were we just looking to make money?

434
00:39:46,880 --> 00:39:51,190
If it was to make money, then I would've sold my patent back then.

435
00:39:51,190 --> 00:39:56,010
If it was to make money, then you could've invested in any other field.

436
00:39:56,010 --> 00:39:59,060
Weren't we doing this to fulfill our dream?

437
00:40:01,150 --> 00:40:03,640
Do you remember our old motto?

438
00:40:03,640 --> 00:40:07,980
"The most outstanding in the industry. No.1 in China. The leader of the world. "

439
00:40:07,980 --> 00:40:10,120
"The most outstanding in the industry"? We did it!

440
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:12,900
We are just one step away from being the "No. 1 in China."

441
00:40:12,900 --> 00:40:15,760
Are you really going to leave now?

442
00:40:17,260 --> 00:40:19,630
- I just— 
 - I know, Fang Zhan.

443
00:40:19,630 --> 00:40:21,690
I know.

444
00:40:21,690 --> 00:40:24,030
In the past two years, you've worked especially hard.

445
00:40:24,030 --> 00:40:28,140
I am also impatient, so you've suffered a lot because of me.

446
00:40:28,140 --> 00:40:30,870
Fang Zhan, I promise you

447
00:40:30,870 --> 00:40:33,530
that from now on, I will be more aware

448
00:40:33,530 --> 00:40:35,850
of my work attitude and ways.

449
00:40:35,850 --> 00:40:37,580
GM Pan,

450
00:40:40,260 --> 00:40:42,490
honestly, you've been fine.

451
00:40:47,890 --> 00:40:50,400
Lubao being where it's at today

452
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:52,990
was very difficult.

453
00:40:52,990 --> 00:40:55,720
We must not give up.

454
00:40:55,720 --> 00:40:57,710
Let's continue, okay?

455
00:41:04,380 --> 00:41:09,110
In the next few days, I plan to invite the Board of Directors to a meeting

456
00:41:09,110 --> 00:41:11,040
to discuss Lubao3 again.

457
00:41:11,040 --> 00:41:14,720
I will propose to install another 2 production lines.

458
00:41:14,720 --> 00:41:17,430
I hope that you will support me.

459
00:41:17,430 --> 00:41:19,680
Just like before.

460
00:41:22,860 --> 00:41:25,280
How is Liu Yang?

461
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:27,550
There are a few health indices that haven't dropped to a normal level yet.

462
00:41:27,550 --> 00:41:30,170
The doctors say that he needs to stay in the hospital for a while longer.

463
00:41:30,170 --> 00:41:32,280
I asked around, and people with this sickness

464
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:35,630
cannot get overstimulated or tired. They have to recover slowly.

465
00:41:35,630 --> 00:41:37,740
How are you doing?

466
00:41:39,990 --> 00:41:42,530
Hi, Xiao Liu, long time no see.

467
00:41:43,620 --> 00:41:46,560
Your aunt just got paid. Yuwei, you can order whatever you want to eat.

468
00:41:46,560 --> 00:41:49,630
Aunt, do you have a lot of money?

469
00:41:49,630 --> 00:41:51,640
I want to have a lot of money.

470
00:41:51,640 --> 00:41:54,630
Will you share some with mommy?

471
00:41:54,630 --> 00:41:56,940
Yuwei, what are you saying?

472
00:41:56,940 --> 00:42:00,590
When we were eating fruit, the teacher said

473
00:42:00,590 --> 00:42:05,180
that the kids who cannot finish their fruits can share with the kids who don't have any.

474
00:42:05,180 --> 00:42:07,270
These are not the same things.

475
00:42:07,270 --> 00:42:10,770
- Don't you not have money? 
 - Yuwei!

476
00:42:10,770 --> 00:42:14,370
You are not allowed to talk about it again.

477
00:42:14,370 --> 00:42:16,560
I'll give you another jujube.

478
00:42:22,610 --> 00:42:25,490
[¥2,000] 

479
00:42:29,110 --> 00:42:31,230
Let's take a look.

480
00:42:41,750 --> 00:42:46,260
- Xiaoling.
 -  I've known you since I was 12 years old.

481
00:42:49,800 --> 00:42:53,020
- Thank you. 
 - Why thank me? It's nothing.

482
00:42:53,020 --> 00:42:57,260
I'll just buy one less outfit. Later, I'll have Siyu give you some.

483
00:42:57,260 --> 00:43:00,110
Don't. Please don't tell her about this.

484
00:43:00,110 --> 00:43:01,780
What?

485
00:43:01,780 --> 00:43:05,810
Haven't you notice that she's worried about money?

486
00:43:05,810 --> 00:43:08,480
Doesn't she have a lot of money?

487
00:43:09,950 --> 00:43:13,210
A few days ago, I went to see her.

488
00:43:13,810 --> 00:43:17,250
No wonder she takes my hand moisturizer.

489
00:43:17,250 --> 00:43:21,950
Join my team! Trust me. Within three years, we will definitely be the leading brand

490
00:43:21,950 --> 00:43:24,920
within the car battery service industry.

491
00:43:26,840 --> 00:43:30,460
That's great! We'll meet at the company next Monday then!

492
00:43:37,900 --> 00:43:40,110
Great, I just recruited a talent.

493
00:43:41,510 --> 00:43:43,060
What were we talking about earlier?

494
00:43:43,060 --> 00:43:45,630
To be clear, I am paying today.

495
00:43:45,630 --> 00:43:47,510
If we go by the order, it should be me.

496
00:43:47,510 --> 00:43:49,440
Well, I want to cut in. Is that not allowed?

497
00:43:49,440 --> 00:43:51,370
Fine.

498
00:43:52,210 --> 00:43:54,220
What company is it?

499
00:43:58,630 --> 00:44:01,500
Okay. I got it.

500
00:44:03,930 --> 00:44:06,200
Okay. Thanks.

501
00:44:13,770 --> 00:44:15,530
Siyu...

502
00:44:25,220 --> 00:44:28,540
A friend just told me that during the Lubao bidding crisis,

503
00:44:28,540 --> 00:44:31,900
a company called Langfei spent ¥40,000 on internet ghostwriters

504
00:44:31,900 --> 00:44:34,720
 to post harmful comments about Lubao. 

505
00:45:22,330 --> 00:45:23,970
Come in.

506
00:45:23,970 --> 00:45:25,490
Director Chen, your delivery.

507
00:45:25,490 --> 00:45:26,930
Okay.

508
00:45:29,470 --> 00:45:31,600
I didn't order food, did I?

509
00:45:31,600 --> 00:45:34,110
- Did you order it for me? 
 - Not me.

510
00:45:34,110 --> 00:45:36,430
All right. You can go back to work now.

511
00:45:50,390 --> 00:45:56,320
 Eat well, exercise well, rest well, and work well!

